description:
Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of Atlanta, plus Dorinda Medley stops by to talk all about season 2 of The Real Housewives Ultimate Girls Trip: Ex-Wives Club, which premieres on June 23rd on Peacock! Dorinda also touches on RHONY Legacy, her relationships with her UGT castmates, filming at Blue Stone Manor, and more!


DORINDA INTERVIEW: 16:20ish
